generalDescription: This test case describes when a patient is administered the first and second dose of a two-dose Non-US Covid-19 vaccine (e.g Astra Zeneca), but still a WHO Covid-19 vaccine, and a booster dose of the Pfizer Covid-19 Bivalent vaccine that the doses are valid.  Series is complete.  Patient is up to date.
